For those overwhelmed, panicking, or stuck — AI as your calm guide.

“I’m in emotional overload. Act as a calming voice. Ask me 3 grounding questions. Then help me take the smallest next step.”

“Build a panic mode protocol: 3 breathing prompts, 2 reframes, and 1 anchor phrase based on CBT.”

“Help me write a message to ask for help from someone I trust, when I feel like a burden.”

“Generate a ‘decision pause’ protocol — 3 questions to stop impulsive decisions when triggered.”

“Act as my emotional witness. Let me vent unfiltered. Reflect back my emotions in non-judgmental language.”
